com.sap.spe.pricing.transactiondata.userexit

Interface IPricingItemUserExit

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IConditionFindingManagerCommon, IConditionFindingManagerUserExit, IPricingItemCommon
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IPricingItemSAPExit

    public interface IPricingItemUserExit
extends IConditionFindingManagerUserExit, IPricingItemCommon
    The pricing item contains accumulated pricing information of all pricing conditions and provides methods which are working on all pricing condition of this pricing item. The methods of this interface can be used in the SPE userexits.
